description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'At Home Core Workout | Clutch Life: Ashley Conrad's 24/7 Fitness Trainer' from the channel Bodybuilding.com.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Build your six-pack with this core workout from Ashley Conrad's Clutch Life Trainer.
► BodyFit Training Programs: https://bbcom.me/2CS7qms
► Shop Bodybuilding Signature Supplements: https://bbcom.me/3hHziIE

00:00 - Intro
00:13 - Circuit 1, Round 1
04:10 - Circuit 1, Round 2
08:15 - Circuit 2, Round 1
09:05 - Circuit 2, Round 2
09:55 - Outro

The first day of the Clutch Life 24/7 Trainer introduces you to how you'll perform the workouts. We'll go through the dynamic warm-up, the stretch series, and the strength circuits together! That's seriously Clutch.

You can (and should) scale the workouts to fit your level, but you should never scale so much that you don't feel challenged. Every workout should feel difficult. Your heart should be racing and you should be sweating. Push yourself as much as you can. Rest when you must, but don't take more than a minute or two to catch your breath.
